'''Mairin''' is a mermaid, located underwater by the shores of [[Fossil Island]]. She runs a [[Mairin's Market|market]] which sells a variety of [[underwater]]-related items, bought with [[mermaid's tear]]s. She can also train the player's [[Agility]] and [[Thieving]] in exchange for [[glistening tear]]s. Both tears are obtained by searching chests and clams in the [[Underwater#Mermaid's_domain|mermaid's domain]].

Mairin objects to [[fishbowl helmet]]s and does not allow players to use them when talking to her or when going to the mermaid's domain, as her sister was once trapped in a fishbowl helmet by humans.

